(542, 5, '2014-05-08 03:11:54', '2014-05-08 03:11:54', 'TOPSHOTS\n\nView of houses in flames during a fire in Valparaiso, 110 km west of Santiago, Chile, on April 12, 2014. Authorities decreed a red alert for the area after the fire consumed more than 100 houses.   AFP PHOTO / ALBERTO MIRANDA\n\n TOPSHOTS-CHILE-FIRE TOPSHOTS-CHILE-FIRE', 'TOPSHOTSView of houses in flames during a fire in Valparaiso', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'topshotsview-of-houses-in-flames-during-a-fire-in-valparaiso', '', '', '2014-05-08 03:11:54', '2014-05-08 03:11:54', '', 540, 'http://vergel439.cl/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/1929000.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
